articles.title: Saudi Arabia certain to host 2034 FIFA World Cup as Australia drops out - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Saudi Arabia’s bid to host the 2034 World Cup will go uncontested after Australia dropped out.
articles.content:
Saudi Arabia is all but certain to host the mens 2034 FIFA World Cup after the Australian football federation declined to enter the bidding contest.
